corn job is linux command for scheduling  a task it will Automat  the services which we can manually set in the format of corn job
*                  *                   *                *                   *
minutes          hours                day of the month  month           day  of the weekend  all are starts from zero 
# check corn job service on linux system 
sudo systemctl status corn.service 
cat /etc/corntab
corntab -l
